Vivo,is,a,school,rewards,system,in,which,educators,set,goals,and,students,earn,points,Vivos,for,achieving,those,goals,Students,can,then,turn,in,Vivos,for,various,rewards,The,Vivo,API,allows,developers,to,access,information,stored,within,the,Vivo,system,Exposed,resources,include,user,data,transactions,award,information,reward,management,and,search,functionality